{"tid":40918,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"《男子之身卻載著女子之心》","createTime":"2016-12-15T13:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T14:10:14.000Z","uid":1714,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"651587637db4b13828856e9b4738d20806b38cb5","tid":40918,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"我第一次係討論區寫文㗎乍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果寫得唔好請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n  光陰荏苒，原來曦兒已在世上活著了十四個歲月，同時也象徵著她以女子之身活了十四年，噢不對，正確點來說，是他活了十四年。<br />\n<br />\n  曦兒自小就失去了父母，那是一次的意外，意外發生在曦兒出生以前，正正因為這個意外，使她的一生有著翻天覆地的變化。<br />\n<br />\n  自從那次意外以後，曦兒一直寄居在她姑媽的家裏，日久生情，她的姑媽在婚後都沒有孩子，因此曦兒就像她的親生女兒一樣，受到她的愛戴。<br />\n<br />\n  今天曦兒如常的上學，她就讀的是九龍區的某所女名校，穿上校服的她總羡煞旁人。<br />\n<br />\n  「我出門口啦！」穿上筆直旗袍校服的曦兒，如常在七時十五分出門，正正是這個準時出門的習慣，使她在旁人的印象中從來沒有遲到過。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n有人會睇我先再寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca0a3c2cf584a8ddfc074f2ceb17cff588b39d8","tid":40918,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T13:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef77510b47c559024be287c1883d9db17769230","tid":40918,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a61845ae94a43a29c0cef91b69f21e0e96a8cf1","tid":40918,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:10:14.000Z